direction: right

*.style.border-radius: 8
*.style.font-size: 13
*.style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
*.style.stroke: "#333333"

# --- Entry ---

entry: |md
  **strategy-testability-review**

  - [RHAISTRAT-NNNN] or all
  - context: fork · model opus
  - invoked by /strategy-review
  - test-engineer lens (Read/Grep/Glob)
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Mode decision ---

mode: |md
  **Mode?**
  local/strat-tasks exists?
| {
  shape: diamond
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Read inputs (local) ---

read-local: |md
  **Read inputs (local)**

  - local/strat-tasks/
  - local/strat-originals/ (RFE)
  - local/strat-reviews/ (prior)
  - $ARGUMENTS: one key vs all
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Read inputs (CI) ---

read-ci: |md
  **Read inputs (CI)**

  - artifacts/strat-tasks/
  - artifacts/rfe-tasks/ (RFE)
  - artifacts/strat-reviews/ (prior)
  - $ARGUMENTS: one key vs all
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Cross-reference ---

xref: |md
  **Cross-ref RFE + prior reviews**

  - map to original acceptance criteria
  - re-review? addressed / still open
  - new issues from revisions
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Assess testability (LLM) ---

assess: |md
  **Assess testability**
  test-engineer lens

  - criteria testable &amp; measurable?
  - missing edge cases / failure modes
  - test strategy (unit / integ / e2e)
  - NFRs quantified w/ numeric thresholds
  - each threshold cites a grounded source
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- Structured verdict ---

output-verdict: |md
  **Structured verdict**
  per strategy

  - Testability
  - Missing edge cases
  - Untestable criteria
  - Test complexity
  - Recommendation
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Flow ---

entry -> mode
mode -> read-local: "local"
mode -> read-ci: "CI (artifacts)"
read-local -> xref
read-ci -> xref
xref -> assess
assess -> output-verdict
